CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1775221865
OL,3,CFlights cancellations begin in UK due
OL,4,Cto impact of Iran war
OL,6,FFlight cancellations have begun in the
OL,7,FUK due to the impact on fuel caused by
OL,8,Fthe US-Israeli war in Iran.
OL,10,FRegional airline Skybus announced its
OL,11,Fflights between Cornwall Airport
OL,12,FNewquay and London Gatwick would be
OL,13,Fabruptly cancelled starting from April
OL,14,F2, due to "circumstances beyond our
OL,15,Fcontrol".
OL,17,FCustomers expecting to travel in April
OL,18,Fand May are being contacted by the
OL,19,Fairline, and will receive a full
OL,20,Frefund, the airline said.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,314,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31302
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1775221865
OL,3,CFlights cancellations begin in UK due
OL,4,Cto impact of Iran war
OL,6,FManaging director Jonathan Hinkles
OL,7,Fblamed the "huge rise in the cost of
OL,8,Ffuel following the war in the Gulf" as
OL,9,Fwell as a drop in passenger bookings.
OL,11,F"At a time of great economic
OL,12,Funcertainty and steps being taken to
OL,13,Fconserve energy worldwide, it is
OL,14,Fneither environmentally nor
OL,15,Feconomically sound for us to continue
OL,16,Fflying with vastly reduced passenger
OL,17,Fnumbers," Hinkles said.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
