OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1775221865
OL,3,CFlights cancellations begin in UK due
OL,4,Cto impact of Iran war
OL,6,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,7,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,8,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,9,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,11,FGuernsey airline Aurigny said last
OL,12,Fweek it would be reducing flights
OL,13,Fbetween the island and London City
OL,14,Fairport between mid-April and early
OL,15,FJune, as well as combining services to
OL,16,Fand from South-West England between
OL,17,FExeter and Bristol.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,314,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31304
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1775221865
OL,3,CFlights cancellations begin in UK due
OL,4,Cto impact of Iran war
OL,6,FMost of the airline's Wednesday
OL,7,Fflights to and from Paris, in France,
OL,8,Fhave also been put back until June, it
OL,9,Fsaid.
OL,11,FThe airline is also adding a temporary
OL,12,Ffuel adjustment surcharge of #2 on all
OL,13,Fbookings made from March 20 onwards.
OL,15,F"With no immediate end to the regional
OL,16,Fconflict in the Middle East in sight,
OL,17,Faviation fuel prices have also
OL,18,Fincreased considerably and show
OL,19,Fcontinued extreme daily fluctuations,"
OL,20,Fa spokesperson for Aurigny said.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,314,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31305
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1775221865
OL,3,CFlights cancellations begin in UK due
OL,4,Cto impact of Iran war
OL,6,FCustomers affected by the changes are
OL,7,Fbeing contacted directly by the
OL,8,Fairline.
OL,10,F"While a small island community, we
OL,11,Fare not immune to the realities
OL,12,Fpresented by the global travel
OL,13,Fecosystem," Philip Saunders, Aurigny's
OL,14,Fchief commercial officer said.
OL,16,F"Current global events are impacting
OL,17,Fconsumer confidence and changing
OL,18,Ftravel behaviours. Furthermore,
OL,19,Fsignificant increases in global oil
OL,20,Fprices are now filtering through to
OL,21,Faviation.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,314,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31306
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1775221865
OL,3,CFlights cancellations begin in UK due
OL,4,Cto impact of Iran war
OL,6,F"Unfortunately, we have to pass on
OL,7,Fsome of the resulting costs to
OL,8,Fcustomers to ensure sustainable air
OL,9,Fservices to and from Guernsey."
OL,11,FSaunders said the airline hoped to
OL,12,Fwelcome back UK holidaymakers from
OL,13,FJuly onwards.
OL,15,FNo British airlines have cancelled
OL,16,Fflights as of yet. British Airways
OL,17,Ftold ITV News: "UK airlines are
OL,18,Fcurrently not seeing disruption to jet
OL,19,Ffuel supply and continue to engage
OL,20,Fwith fuel suppliers and government to
OL,21,Fmonitor the situation."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,314,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31307
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1775221865
OL,3,CFlights cancellations begin in UK due
OL,4,Cto impact of Iran war
OL,6,FThe Iran war has had a global impact
OL,7,Fon fuel and energy prices as the
OL,8,FStrait of Hormuz - a major waterway,
OL,9,Fthrough which a fifth of the world's
OL,10,Foil travels - remains largely shut.
OL,12,FThe price of Brent crude oil, the
OL,13,Fworld's benchmark, has soared to
OL,14,Fhigher than $100 a barrel during the
OL,15,Fwar for the first time since 2022.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,314,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31308
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1775221865
OL,3,CFlights cancellations begin in UK due
OL,4,Cto impact of Iran war
OL,6,FRyanair boss Michael O'Leary warned on
OL,7,FWednesday that high jet fuel prices
OL,8,Fcould cause disruptions in May and
OL,9,FJune if the war does not come to an
OL,10,Fend soon, with the UK hardest hit in
OL,11,FEurope.
OL,13,F"Of all the European countries at the
OL,14,Fmoment, the one that is most
OL,15,Fvulnerable is the UK because of the
OL,16,Fmarket share that the Kuwaitis have
OL,17,Fhere," O'Leary said.
OL,26,@yD@FO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,314,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31309
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1775221865
OL,3,CFlights cancellations begin in UK due
OL,4,Cto impact of Iran war
OL,6,F"There could be a surplus of jet A-1
OL,7,Ffuel in the Middle East, but you have
OL,8,Fstill got to ship it to Europe and we
OL,9,Fdon't know when or how that happens."
OL,11,FMultiple other countries have already
OL,12,Fseen flight cancellations due to the
OL,13,Fwar, with Air New Zealand announcing
OL,14,Fon March 12 it was axing 1,100 flights
OL,15,Funtil early May over jet fuel prices.
OL,17,FVietnamese airlines have cut flights
OL,18,Fon domestic and international routes,
OL,19,Fand some regional routes across
OL,20,FAustralia are not being flown.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
